  "title": "Project Coordinator / Scrum Master",
  "description": "<p><strong>Project Coordinator / Scrum Master</strong></p><p><strong>Role:</strong>\nProject Coordinator / Scrum\nMaster<br />\n<br />\n</p><p><strong>Role Overview</strong></p><p>Drive Agile delivery execution, sprint\ngovernance, and cross-team coordination for enterprise digital transformation programs.\nEnsure delivery predictability, dependency management, and continuous\nimprovement across multi-vendor teams.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Facilitate Agile ceremonies (Sprint Planning, Stand-ups,\n     Reviews, Retrospectives).</li><li>Track sprint commitments, velocity, delivery metrics, risks and\n     dependencies.</li><li>Remove impediments and manage cross-team dependencies.</li><li>Maintain delivery plans, RAID logs, and release readiness.</li><li>Coordinate across business, vendors, architects, QA, DevOps and\n     infrastructure teams.</li><li>Produce delivery dashboards and management reports.</li><li>Support release coordination, environment readiness, and\n     go-live activities.</li></ul><p><strong>Mandatory Skills</strong></p><ul><li>5+ years as Scrum Master / Project Coordinator.</li><li>Strong Agile/Scrum delivery experience.</li><li>Excellent stakeholder coordination skills.</li><li>Jira / Confluence proficiency.</li><li>Strong reporting and planning skills.</li><li>Insurance or financial services exposure.</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred</strong></p><ul><li>Large-scale transformation program experience.</li><li>SAFe / enterprise Agile exposure.</li></ul>",
